Question 1


house_trim <- house %>% 
  select(price, everything(),
         -c(id, date, sqft_living15, sqft_lot15, zipcode)) %>% 
  mutate(waterfront = as.logical(waterfront),
         renovated = if_else(yr_renovated == 0, FALSE, TRUE)) %>% 
  select(-yr_renovated) %>% 
  mutate(grade = case_when(
    grade <= 3 ~ "poor",
    grade <= 7 ~ "average",
    grade <= 13 ~ "great"
  ),
  price = log(price),
  bedrooms = log(bedrooms+0.01))

house_trim %>% 
  skim()
